"content": "<p>A substance remarkable for its transparency. Two phenomena seen by John in his vision in the book of Revelation are likened to glass.</p>\n<h2>The sea of glass</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:2\">REV 15:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:2-Rev4:6\">REV 4:2–4:6</a></p>\n<h2>The gold in the new Jerusalem likened to glass</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:21\">REV 21:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:15-Rev21:18\">REV 21:15–21:18</a></p>",
